      <title>TVA 斥资 3.5 亿美元开发小型核反应堆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/tva-spending-350-million-to-develop-small-nuclear-reactors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[田纳西河谷管理局批准再拨款 1.5 亿美元支持先进核技术，以满足人口增长带来的电力需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/tva-spending-350-million-to-develop-small-nuclear-reactors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 20:10:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷参议院无视 Milei 法案通过新养老金方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/argentina-senate-passes-new-pension-formula-in-defiance-of-milei</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷参议员周四批准了一项法案，该法案违背了总统哈维尔·米莱通过重新制定养老金计算方式来平衡政府收支的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/argentina-senate-passes-new-pension-formula-in-defiance-of-milei</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 20:09:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党大会避免就加沙问题展开辩论，力争团结在哈里斯身后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/democrats-avoid-gaza-debate-in-convention-push-to-unify-behind-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡马拉·哈里斯在民主党全国代表大会上面对加沙战争这一政治敏感问题的竞选策略基本上是完全避免面对它。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/democrats-avoid-gaza-debate-in-convention-push-to-unify-behind-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 19:13:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯在总统提名之路上无视质疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/harris-defies-doubters-on-road-to-presidential-nomination</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡玛拉·哈里斯将于周四在民主党全国代表大会上发表主旨演讲，届时她将巩固自己令人惊叹的政治转型：从一位竞选和领导能力一直受到民主党同僚质疑的副总统，转变为一位掌控新兴政党的候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/harris-defies-doubters-on-road-to-presidential-nomination</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 18:48:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉斯维加斯靠小费生活的工人怀疑免税宣传的真实性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/vegas-workers-who-live-off-tips-doubt-reality-of-tax-free-pitches</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从代客泊车的服务员到二十一点赌台的发牌人，再到城里众多酒吧的调酒师，拉斯维加斯都依赖于人们工作来赚取小费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/vegas-workers-who-live-off-tips-doubt-reality-of-tax-free-pitches</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 17:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>移民问题加剧 瑞士人口激增 创 1960 年代以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/swiss-population-jumps-most-since-1960s-amid-immigration-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士人口增幅达到半个多世纪以来的最高水平，这进一步加剧了有关该国是否应该向移民敞开大门的争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/swiss-population-jumps-most-since-1960s-amid-immigration-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 14:48:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>他信提出拯救泰国摆脱债务陷阱的策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/thaksin-pitches-strategy-to-rescue-thailand-from-debt-trap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前总理他信·西那瓦表示，泰国需要紧急解决高额家庭和公共债务问题，并集中精力制定政策，推动泰国经济增速与一些东南亚邻国相媲美。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/thaksin-pitches-strategy-to-rescue-thailand-from-debt-trap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 12:56:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪访问基辅前强调外交优先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/modi-calls-for-peace-diplomacy-ahead-of-his-visit-to-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在 2022 年俄罗斯军队入侵后首次访问基辅之前重申，乌克兰战争只能通过外交方式解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/modi-calls-for-peace-diplomacy-ahead-of-his-visit-to-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 04:54:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大铁路公司拒绝工会工人上班，贸易陷入混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/canada-railways-lock-out-workers-as-talks-fail-snarling-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大两条最大的铁路公司于周四凌晨在与工会领导人的谈判失败后关闭，立即阻断了北美供应链的主干道，这些供应链每天的贸易额约为 10 亿加元（7.4 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/canada-railways-lock-out-workers-as-talks-fail-snarling-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 04:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
